title: Dizzee Rascal - 2007- Maths and English
description:
Dylan Mills - known professionally as Dizzee Rascal - is an English rapper and record producer. His largely self-composed music is a blend of garage MCing, conventional rap, grime and ragga, with extremely eclectic samples and more exotic styles.

Dizzee&#039;s third album Maths + English was released on June 4, 2007. He stated in an interview before the album&#039;s release that "Maths" refers to producing, in terms of beats, deals and money and "English" to writing lyrics.
